  "text": "For the CFMT, the method was as described in [CITATION_1] . Briefly, participants learned six Caucasian male faces-each in three views, to encourage face rather than image learning. Participants later discriminated these targets from similar-looking distractor faces (untimed threealternative, forced-choice task, with simultaneous presentation of the faces; Fig. 4a ). The CFMT has good psychometric properties and produces large individual differences [CITATION_2] Wilmer et al., 2010) .",
